name: Bossk
Lore: 'Male Trandoshan bounty hunter. Strong but clumsy. Extremely proud and arrogant. Suffered a humiliating defeat at the hands of Chewbacca and his partner Han Solo.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Hound''s Tooth, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. Adds 1 to attrition against opponent in battles at same site. While present, may reduce Chewie''s forfeit to zero while here.',
